Program: Start the Week
Title: The Language of Money
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b04n304k
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 3 Nov 2014
'Money talks' in a special edition of Start the Week recorded in front of an audience at Radio 3's Free Thinking Festival at Sage Gateshead. Anne McElvoy explores the language and morality of money, from the super-rich to zombie debt, with the writers John Lanchester and Naomi Alderman, plus the journalists Martin Wolf and John Kampfner. Producer: Simon Tillotson. Show less